    <body>
        <p>The page breaks can be controlled in multiple ways:</p>
        <ol id="ol_yjd_cf4_vcb">
            <li>By creating an <codeph>@page</codeph> and assigning it to an element will create a
        page break between this element and the sibling elements that have a different page.</li>
            <li>Using the CSS properties: <codeph>page-break-before</codeph>
        <codeph>page-break-after</codeph>.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
